    {
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "chapterTitle": "三、事实不清、证据不足的死刑案件及其应对",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "41787997_13_432-510",
          "range": "432-510",
          "rangeStart": 432,
          "rangeEnd": 510,
          "markText": "事实不清，证据不足的死刑案件，对我们来讲，辩护的空间就会更大一些。我们的工作就是要去放大它的事实不清，放大它的证据不足。怎样放大？我觉得有几点是可以做到的。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1723176173,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-09 12:02:53",
          "chapterUid": 13,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41787997&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=432&rangeEnd=510",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0232330727da25df025d59?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=432&rangeEnd=510"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "chapterTitle": "阅卷的多个层次",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "41787997_15_16499-16633",
          "range": "16499-16633",
          "rangeStart": 16499,
          "rangeEnd": 16633,
          "markText": "说到这里，我想提示大家有时候说话要注意一些技巧，该快的时候快，该慢的时候要慢，慎之又慎，尤其是避免一些比较敏感和过激的言语。所以，在法庭上说话速度要有意放慢，至少比正常讲话语速慢一倍，因为语速放慢，",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1723176172,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-09 12:02:52",
          "chapterUid": 15,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41787997&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=16499&rangeEnd=16633",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0232330727da25df025d59?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=16499&rangeEnd=16633"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "41787997_15_10364-10388",
          "range": "10364-10388",
          "rangeStart": 10364,
          "rangeEnd": 10388,
          "markText": "军事参谋学里常讲到，“人在路上走，心在图中移”，",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1723176172,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-09 12:02:52",
          "chapterUid": 15,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41787997&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=10364&rangeEnd=10388",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0232330727da25df025d59?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=10364&rangeEnd=10388"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
